commit: Fix the combination number calculation to use the BigDecimal numbers.
Fix links to the combinations section in the readme file.
Fix issue #14 getNumberOfGeneratedObjects() returns long; ints only accepted by generateObjectsRange(). https://github.com/dpaukov/combinatoricslib/issues/14

1. Fixed exception in CombinatoricsVector when input Vector has null elements. 2. Allow to generate complex combinations when requested combination length is more then the size of the original vector and excludeEmptySet is false.

Added an example of using the permutations, combinations and subsets generators. A method generates the n compositions (with fixed length) in relation with permutations. Example: From the ordered list {a,b,b,c} of length 4, generate all compositions with 2 (ordered) sublists which include all the elements of the original list in sum. {{a},{b,b,c}} {{a,b},{b,c}} {{a,c},{b,b}} {{a,b,b},{c}} {{a,b,c},{b}} {{b},{a,b,c}} {{b,b},{a,c}} {{b,c},{a,b}} {{b,b,c},{a}} {{c},{a,b,b}}
